# CLAUDE.md

Place your personal CLAUDE.md here. The setup script will copy it to ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md on first boot.

This file is gitignored — copy your own CLAUDE.md to claude-config/CLAUDE.md before building the USB:

    cp ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md claude-config/CLAUDE.md

See https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code for CLAUDE.md documentation.
